        "Id": "ec05bb45-d2c8-4df7-96b6-00fb6c803968",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "The Final Trick",
        "Location": "LOCATION_COASTALTOWN",
        "PublicId": "103464053413",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_octopus.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 9ba668f0-842c-457f-a999-20d3fb414fd0).Image",
        "Description": "The stage is set, the crowd is watching, and the magician is ready. Only this time, it&apos;s you behind the curtain. Your target: a group of women enchanted by the talents of a local street performer. Your mission: make them vanish, permanently.\r\rInfiltrate the performance, assume the role of the magician, and deliver the final act they’ll never forget. No props. No applause. Just silence.\r\rRemember 47, true magic leaves no witnesses.",
